videos.headline: Kelley leaps for the TD
videos.description: UCLA RB Joshua Kelley dives for the touchdown as UCLA capitalizes on ASU's turnover on the previous drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Kelley leaps for the TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kelley barrels into the end zone
videos.description: Joshua Kelley grabs his second touchdown of the first quarter as UCLA takes a 14-7 lead over Arizona State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Kelley barrels into the end zone) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA's Kelley picks up hat-trick in 1st half
videos.description: Joshua Kelley's dominant first half continues as he scores his third rushing touchdown, giving UCLA the 21-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (UCLA's Kelley picks up hat-trick in 1st half) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson-Robinson finds Philips for a UCLA TD
videos.description: UCLA's dominant 1st half ends with Dorian Thompson-Robinson tossing a touchdown to Kyle Phillips.
